{{about||Netflix original TV shows|List of original programs distributed by Netflix|Netflix original stand-up comedy specials|List of original stand-up comedy specials distributed by Netflix}}
[[File:Netflix 2015 logo.svg|frameless|right|alt=Netflix 2015 logo]]
[[Netflix]] is an American global on-demand Internet [[streaming media]] provider, that has distributed a number of original programs, including original [[List of original programs distributed by Netflix|series]], specials (including [[List of original stand-up comedy specials distributed by Netflix|stand-up comedy specials]]), [[miniseries]], [[Documentary film|documentaries]], and films. Netflix's original films also include content that was first screened in other countries for exclusive broadcast in other territories, which is branded in those regions as Netflix original content.

